metadata.dc:author: Howell Aguilar, A L
Günther Nonell, J
metadata.dc:description: From a comparative point of view the axonal cytology and the ultrastructure of Ranvier nodes in non-giant myelinated fibers of the shrimp Penaeus are described.
metadata.dc:title: Ultraestructura de los nudos de Ranvier en fibras nerviosas mielinizadas del camarón Penaeus.
[Ultrastructure of the Ranvier's nodes in myelinated nerve fibers of the shrimp Penaeus].
